Services : <linebreak/>
 /user_interface</para>
<para>Clients : /position_server</para>
<para>Action Client : /go_to_point</para>
<para>Description :</para>
<para>This node implements the finite state machine for the input on the control of the holonomic robot. It includes:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>An Action client &quot;go_to_point&quot; that interacts with the action &quot;Planning&quot; to:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>set a new goal</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>check if the goal has been reached</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>check if the goal has been cancelled</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Define the new state</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>A Service server that advertise the command line user interface</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>A Service client that requires a new target postion from the /position_server </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
